oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Farewell to the Goodies (0646)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Concerts;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and blue on white) announcing Farewell to Goodies [Warehouse] New Years Eve celebration with Stillhouse Reelers and others at the Main street Cafe on December 31. Poster is a template for pole cards. Poster features a woodcut of a musician.
